posting_body: ['Welcome to Excalibur Apartments!', 'Call for More Details:', 'show contact info', '<URL>', 'Urban living in the heart of beautiful downtown Bellevue!', 'Be in the center of city living without the high cost!', 'Excalibur features Studio, One & Two Bedroom floorplans that fit any budget!', 'Located minutes to Bellevue Square Mall, Meydenbauer Convention Center, acclaimed restaurants and more!', 'Walking distance to restaurants, theaters, and close to convenient bus stops and future lightrail!', 'We have a plethora of layouts that will accommodate your every need.', 'Let us give you a tour and you can choose the home of your dreams.', 'These floor plans accommodate to your lifestyle.', 'Apartment 429 is a large studio with 3 closets, including a', 'walk-in closet', ", that overlooks the community's courtyard.", 'As it is tucked away from traffic noise the home stays quieter.', 'Its floorplan is open and convenient with full -sized in-unit laundry and a spectacular location in downtown Bellevue.', 'Apply now to secure this home and enjoy a waived $250 administration fee and a refunded application fee!', 'Amenities:', 'Excellent Location in downtown Bellevue', 'Pet Friendly', 'Cardio/Exercise Center', 'Convenient 3 level', 'Reserved', 'Parking Garage', '2 Elevators', 'Vending Room', 'Package Receiving', 'Cats & Small Dogs Welcome', 'Centralized Courtyard', 'On Site & Helpful Maintenance Staff', 'Professional & Friendly Management', 'Close to Freeways – I405, 520 & I90!', 'Quick Access to Public Transportation', 'Energy Efficient Forced Air Heating', 'Frost Free Refrigerator', 'Self Cleaning Oven', 'In-Unit Laundry Included', 'Wheelchair Access', 'Disposal', 'Dishwasher', 'Cable & Internet Ready', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
